# FRONTEND — Next.js / React

## Framework & Versions
- Next.js 14 with App Router. Never use Pages Router.
- React 18.
- Tailwind CSS v4 with @theme directive in globals.css (not tailwind.config.js).
- TypeScript.
- framer-motion for ProgressBar animation only.

## App Directory Structure (exact)
frontend/
├── app/
│   ├── layout.tsx           # Root layout: bg-bg-primary, font-sans, data-theme="dark"
│   ├── page.tsx             # Redirect to /dashboard
│   ├── dashboard/page.tsx   # JobInputPanel + JobList
