## State Management Rules
- Use React Context + useReducer. Never Redux, Zustand, Jotai, or Recoil.
- JobsContext actions: ADD_JOB | UPDATE_JOB_STATUS | SET_JOBS | DELETE_JOB.
- Local component state via useState for UI-only concerns.

## API Communication Rules
- Use native fetch exclusively. Never axios or any HTTP library.
- API base URL from env: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL (default: http://localhost:8000)
- WebSocket URL from env: NEXT_PUBLIC_WS_URL (default: ws://localhost:8000)

## Component Rules

### JobInputPanel
- State: url: string, isLoading: boolean, error: string | null
- NO AggressionSelector. aggression_level does not exist in this UI.
- On submit: POST /api/jobs → router.push(`/jobs/${response.id}`)
- Error display: show under submit button if error !== null, className="text-error text-sm mt-2 text-center"
- Error source: body.detail ?? `Error ${res.status}` or "Network error, please try again"

### JobStatusBadge
- Exactly 4 status mappings (no others):
  pending → { label: 'Queued',     color: 'text-text-secondary bg-border'  }
  running → { label: 'Processing', color: 'text-warn bg-warn/10'           }
  done    → { label: 'Done',       color: 'text-success bg-success/10'     }
  failed  → { label: 'Failed',     color: 'text-error bg-error/10'         }

### ProgressBar
- Uses framer-motion: motion.div animate={{ width: `${progress_pct}%` }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.8, ease: "easeInOut" }}
- STATUS_LABELS defined in ProgressBar.tsx:
  pending='Waiting in queue', running='Processing...', done='Completed', failed='Failed'
- STATUS_LABELS is separate from STATUS_CONFIG in JobStatusBadge.

### LogViewer
- State: logs: string[], wsStatus: 'connecting'|'connected'|'closed'
- WebSocket messages: type='log' → append log. type='done' → read data.status,
  setWsStatus('closed'), ws.close().
- Log level prefix colors: info → text-accent, warn → text-warn, error → text-error.
- Auto-scroll: useRef on container, scrollTop = scrollHeight on each new log.
- Skeleton at wsStatus='connecting': show <SkeletonCard lines={5} />.
- Polling fallback: useInterval(() => fetchJob(id), 3000) when WS unavailable or closed
  (only if job not done/failed).

### SettingsForm
- API key fields: type="password" with show/hide toggle.
- Save active only if isDirty.
- Success: temporary toast "Settings saved" via setTimeout 2000ms.

### SkeletonCard
- Uses Tailwind animate-pulse. No framer-motion.

### DownloadButton
- Renders only if job.status === 'done'.

### not-found.tsx
- On 404 from GET /api/jobs/{id}: call notFound() from next/navigation.
- Container: "flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-bg-primary"
- Link to /dashboard: className includes text-accent hover:text-accent-hover

## Typography (apply via Tailwind classes — exact)
- H1: text-2xl font-semibold text-text-primary tracking-tight
- H2: text-lg font-medium text-text-primary
- Body: text-sm text-text-primary leading-relaxed
- Caption: text-xs text-text-secondary
- Mono (logs, URLs): font-mono text-xs text-text-secondary